content: [TextBlock(text='"Farewell, Tokyo. As I watch the city skyline from Narita airport, I\'m filled with a mix of nostalgia and excitement. Japan\'s blend of tradition and innovation has reshaped my views on tech and life. Heading back to NYC, my mind is buzzing with ideas on how DAOs could revolutionize art collectives. Here\'s to new beginnings, with a touch of the old. 🗾✨"', type='text')]
